CSS code:
/* General Body Styling */
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    background: url('.vscode/f5.gif') no-repeat center center fixed; /* Add your GIF here */
    background-size: cover; /* Cover the entire screen */
    transition: background 2s ease-in-out; /* Smooth transition effect */
    opacity: 0.9; /* Set transparency */
}

/* Hover Effect for Dynamic Transition */
body:hover {
    background-size: 150%; /* Increase size on hover */
    opacity: 0.7; /* Increase transparency on hover */
}

/* Styling for Text Content */
.content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Semi-transparent background for better readability */
    border-radius: 10px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 100px auto;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
}
